						<summary>

						<p>Rock near the Nāga stones at the west end of the tank bund. . • . . • .</p>						

						<p>It is dated in cyclic year Dhātu, Āshāḍha, śu.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged. Seems to register some gifts made by Immaḍi Chikkarāya of the Sugutūri family. Mention Āvulapilli.</p>						

